> Hail Fellow Musicians and Lorekeepers,
>
> I was exploring the Eleven Outpost and found the vendor selling our new
> songs. I compared it to what the Concert Hall had listed and found there
> were 4 more not shown on the Concert Hall List. They are:
>
> L53 Song of the Dawn, Wind
> L58 Jonathan's Inspiration, Brass
> L60 Angstilich's Assonance, Wind
> L60 Kazumi's Preservation, Brass
>
> Also a player was hunting a song called Boombastic Bellow for a quest,
> didn't get any details of what quest he was doing. An npc on one of the
> docks sells a Box of Lute Strings, Unfinished Lute neck, raw bamboo, and
one
> other flute part. I didn't find a bard GM.
>
> Dreadlands: L40 yardtrash, all you can pull and more. I love this zone!
